[a] Devastating outbreak
Date: Mon 19 Apr 2021
Source: Washington Post [abridged, edited]
https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/interactive/2021/india-covid-cases-surge/?utm_campaign=wp_post_most&utm_medium=email&utm_source=newsletter&wpisrc=nl_most&carta-url=


India's devastating outbreak is driving the global coronavirus surge. Those on the country's front lines say the wave is worse than anything they have seen before.

[See article for figures, especially those in the section titled "Northern and Western states are the hardest hit by the new surge in COVID-19 cases in India," which show graphically the daily reported cases per 100 000 people by state. - Mod.LK]

